  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Retail Advertising Service Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Customer Service Executive (Sales Support)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central – Potong Pasir</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Mon-Fri: 9am-6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 2900 + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Serve as the welcoming point of contact for client calls and emails, providing prompt and professional customer support</li><li>Accurately prepare and manage all sales documentation, including quotations, sales orders, purchase orders, and delivery notes</li><li>Support the Sales Team with essential administrative tasks such as reviewing visuals, floor plans, and preparing installation reports</li><li>Coordinate order processing and collaborate with the logistics team to ensure timely deliveries and seamless installations</li><li>Contribute to dynamic, ad-hoc projects and tasks that drive business progress and efficiency</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O level</li><li>Min. 1 year of experience in related field</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Word</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79352 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
